ted subject to terms and conditions of the merchant. The merchant determines and is responsible for the final price and conditions of purchase, including but not limited to, warnings, recalls, disclaimers and usage information. ","textColor":4279440147},{"text":"Learn more","navigationEndpoint":{"clickTrackingParams":"CEMQx1UiEwjlyM-3grGUAxVZdMIBHcRlFnjKAQQ9t74C","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/12257682?nohelpkit=1","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://support.google.com/youtube/answer/12257682?nohelpkit=1","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW"}}},{"text":"\n\nYouTube is not responsible for merchant products or for the product information provided by merchants. YouTube is also not responsible for your activities and purchases made from merchants (including through the links below) which are governed by the respective merchant's terms and conditions (including their Privacy Policy). YouTube may share information with our partners to perform services, in compliance with our Privacy Policy and other appropriate confidentiality and security measures. For instance, YouTube may share your IP address with the merchant platform to facilitate the transaction. Product reviews are available in select locations only and are not verified by Google. ","textColor":4279440147},{"text":"Learn more","navigationEndpoint":{"clickTrackingParams":"CEMQx1UiEwjlyM-3grGUAxVZdMIBHcRlFnjKAQQ9t74C","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://support.google.com/googleshopping/answer/9370999?nohelpkit=1","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://support.google.com/googleshopping/answer/9370999?nohelpkit=1","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW"}}}]},"confirmLabel":{"simpleText":"OK"},"trackingParams":"CEMQx1UiEwjlyM-3grGUAxVZdMIBHcRlFng="}},"popupType":"DIALOG"}},"trackingParams":"CD0Qw9AHGAAiEwjlyM-3grGUAxVZdMIBHcRlFng="}},{"menuServiceItemRenderer":{"tex